latter, from being a hybrid. The name, which is found written Rosamond, Rosamunda, Rosemonde, is of Teutonic origin, having been formed from the old male name Hrosmund, softened down from Ruodmunt, same as the Old and Middle High German name Hrothmond (Icelandic Hrothmundr, Old Gothic Ratmund). Junius translates Ruodmunt 'red mouth;' Wachter, 'vir utilis et consultus.' The name is from ruod-munt for rad-mund, man for counsel, councillor; or from rad-munt, protector in counsel."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Rosamund was born in 1206, in Checkendon, Oxfordshire, England, United Kingdom. She had at least 1 son with Geoffrey Marmion. She died in 1273, in her hometown, at the age of 67."},"et":{"1206–1273":"1206–1273","1198–1246":"1198–1246","1229–1266":"1229–1266","1206":"1206","1246":"1246","1266":"1266","1198":"1198","Abt October 1246":"umbes oktoober 1246","1273":"1273","1229":"1229","Checkenden,Oxford,England":"Oxfordshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Checkendon, Oxfordshire, England":"Checkendon, Oxfordshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Checkenden, Oxfordshire, England":"Checkendon, Oxfordshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1206–1273":"1206–1273","1198–1246":"1198–1246","1229–1266":"1229–1266","1206":"1206","1246":"1246","1266":"1266","1198":"1198","Abt October 1246":"noin lokakuu 1246","1273":"1273","1229":"1229","Checkenden,Oxford,England":"Oxfordshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Checkendon, Oxfordshire, England":"Checkendon, Oxfordshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Checkenden, Oxfordshire, England":"Checkendon, Oxfordshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1206–1273":"1206–1273","1198–1246":"1198–1246","1229–1266":"1229–1266","1206":"1206","1246":"1246","1266":"1266","1198":"1198","Abt October 1246":"environ octobre 1246","1273":"1273","1229":"1229","Checkenden,Oxford,England":"Oxfordshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","Checkendon, Oxfordshire, England":"Checkendon, Oxfordshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","Checkenden, Oxfordshire